snippet.title: Judge Has Officially Sentenced Amber Heard in US Court (+5 YEARS)
snippet.description:
Judge Has Officially Sentenced Amber Heard in US Court (+5 YEARS)

Amber Heard has officially been sentenced by the Judge in the US Court to a maximum of 5 years imprisonment in jail. In most recent times, Johnny Depp has been trying to get more information admitted for his case against Amber, including the potential for her being tried for perjury, and Amber is trying to get the case against her dismissed officially in court. We'll break down all the latest for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

And there you go, peeps! A look at the latest and "greatest" from the court case with Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Do you think that anything that these two are doing in court is going to make a difference in the long run? What are you hoping happens next with all that is going on? Or do you just want it to end?
